{
  "title": "Duck",
  "source": "stardewvalleywiki",
  "data": {
    "parse": {
      "title": "Duck",
      "pageid": 1893,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Duck\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><img alt=\"Duck.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/38/Duck.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"45\" />\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">Happy adults lay duck eggs every other day.  Lives in the coop.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Building\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Big Coop.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d5/Big_Coop.png/24px-Big_Coop.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"28\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d5/Big_Coop.png/36px-Big_Coop.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d5/Big_Coop.png/48px-Big_Coop.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Big Coop</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Purchase Price\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1200 \"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,200g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Produce\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/24px-Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/36px-Duck_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Duck Feather.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/24px-Duck_Feather.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/36px-Duck_Feather.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p>The <b>Duck</b> is an <a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">animal</a> that lives in a <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Big Coop</a>. Ducks can be purchased at <a href=\"/Marnie%27s_Ranch\" title=\"Marnie&#39;s Ranch\">Marnie's Ranch</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1200\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,200g</span> or be hatched by placing a <a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> into an <a href=\"/Incubator\" title=\"Incubator\">Incubator</a>, taking <style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 9,000m (5d 16h 40m)</span> to incubate, or <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 4,500m (2d 21h 40m)</span> with the <a href=\"/Farming#Farming_Skill\" title=\"Farming\">Coopmaster Profession</a>. \n</p><p>Ducks are able to swim in bodies of water on the farm.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Produce\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Produce</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selling\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selling</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Produce\">Produce</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Produce\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Animals#Produce\" title=\"Animals\">Animals#Produce</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Ducks who eat every day mature after 5 nights have passed. A mature and fed duck produces a <a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> every 2 days, which can be placed in an <a href=\"/Incubator\" title=\"Incubator\">Incubator</a> to hatch another duck, or sold for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"95\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />95g</span>. Once sufficient <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">friendship</a> and happiness is reached, a duck may produce a <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a> instead of a Duck Egg, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"250\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />250g</span>.\n</p><p>A Duck Egg can be placed in a <a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a> to produce <a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a>, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"375\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />375g</span>.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Duck_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a>\n</td>\n<td>It's still warm.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/24px-Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/36px-Duck_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>95g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/24px-Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/36px-Duck_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>118g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/24px-Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/36px-Duck_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>142g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/24px-Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/36px-Duck_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>190g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Duck_Feather.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Duck Feather.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>\n</td>\n<td>It's so colorful.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Feather.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/24px-Duck_Feather.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/36px-Duck_Feather.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>250g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Feather.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/24px-Duck_Feather.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/36px-Duck_Feather.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>312g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Feather.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/24px-Duck_Feather.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/36px-Duck_Feather.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>375g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Duck Feather.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/24px-Duck_Feather.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png/36px-Duck_Feather.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f9/Duck_Feather.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>500g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selling\">Selling</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selling\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>It is possible to sell Ducks. The amount of <a href=\"/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> obtained for doing so is dependent on how many hearts the animal has. The more hearts; the higher amount of gold fetched for selling it. The amount of gold obtained for selling a maximum-heart Duck is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1560\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,560g</span> and for a recently hatched Baby Duck without any hearts <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"395\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />395g</span>.\n</p><p>To sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much the animal can be sold for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>In the game, the female, egg-laying ducks have green heads. In actuality, male <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mallard\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Mallard\">Mallard ducks</a> have the characteristic green heads. Females are brown. However, domesticated Cayuga ducks have green feathers in both genders.</li>\n<li>Ducklings make the same noises as adult ducks.</li>\n<li>Ducklings will follow fully grown ducks around the farm.</li>\n<li>Ducks are unique in that if they swim on water, such as on the <a href=\"/Farm_Pond\" title=\"Farm Pond\">Farm Pond</a>, <a href=\"/Farm_Maps\" title=\"Farm Maps\">Riverland or Beach Farms</a>, they do not need to eat <a href=\"/Hay\" title=\"Hay\">hay</a> or <a href=\"/Grass\" title=\"Grass\">grass</a> to be fed overnight. This is indicated by a pecking animation while the duck floats on the surface.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Duck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Lowered purchase price from <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"4000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />4,000g</span> to <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1200\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,200g</span>.  Increased Duck Feather price from <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"125\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />125g</span> to <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"250\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />250g</span>. Ducks can now swim in water.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5.2\" title=\"Version History\">1.5.2</a>: Lowered sell price from <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"5200\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />5,200g</span> to <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1560\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,560g</span>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Ostrich\" title=\"Ostrich\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413230345\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.172 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.673 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 4350/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 18603/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2445/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 5688/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.008/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 740 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  439.917      1 -total\n 39.32%  172.997      1 Template:Infobox_animal\n 38.14%  167.776      2 Template:Qualityprice\n 22.76%  100.110      3 Template:Description\n 12.73%   56.004      8 Template:Overlayimg\n 12.46%   54.802      3 Template:Name\n  7.17%   31.541      2 Template:History\n  5.30%   23.297      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  2.45%   10.775      2 Template:Duration\n  2.15%    9.456      2 Template:Version\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1893-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413230344 and revision id 182104\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox animal\n|image    = Duck.png\n|buyprice = 1200\n|building = {{Name|Big Coop}}\n|produce  = {{Name|Duck Egg}}{{Name|Duck Feather}}\n}}\nThe '''Duck''' is an [[Animals|animal]] that lives in a [[Coop|Big Coop]]. Ducks can be purchased at [[Marnie's Ranch]] for {{Price|1200}} or be hatched by placing a [[Duck Egg]] into an [[Incubator]], taking {{duration|9,000m (5d 16h 40m)|class=inline}} to incubate, or {{duration|4,500m (2d 21h 40m)|class=inline}} with the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Coopmaster Profession]]. \n\nDucks are able to swim in bodies of water on the farm.\n\n==Produce==\n{{main article|Animals#Produce}}\nDucks who eat every day mature after 5 nights have passed. A mature and fed duck produces a [[Duck Egg]] every 2 days, which can be placed in an [[Incubator]] to hatch another duck, or sold for {{Price|95}}. Once sufficient [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]] and happiness is reached, a duck may produce a [[Duck Feather]] instead of a Duck Egg, which sells for {{Price|250}}.\n\nA Duck Egg can be placed in a [[Mayonnaise Machine]] to produce [[Duck Mayonnaise]], which sells for {{Price|375}}.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Duck Egg.png]]\n|[[Duck Egg]]\n|{{Description|Duck Egg}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Duck Egg|95|dsv=false}}\n|-\n|[[File:Duck Feather.png]]\n|[[Duck Feather]]\n|{{Description|Duck Feather}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Duck Feather|250|dsv=false}}\n|}\n\n==Selling==\nIt is possible to sell Ducks. The amount of [[gold]] obtained for doing so is dependent on how many hearts the animal has. The more hearts; the higher amount of gold fetched for selling it. The amount of gold obtained for selling a maximum-heart Duck is {{Price|1560}} and for a recently hatched Baby Duck without any hearts {{Price|395}}.\n\nTo sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much the animal can be sold for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n\n==Trivia==\n* In the game, the female, egg-laying ducks have green heads. In actuality, male [[wikipedia:Mallard|Mallard ducks]] have the characteristic green heads. Females are brown. However, domesticated Cayuga ducks have green feathers in both genders.\n* Ducklings make the same noises as adult ducks.\n* Ducklings will follow fully grown ducks around the farm.\n* Ducks are unique in that if they swim on water, such as on the [[Farm Pond]], [[Farm Maps|Riverland or Beach Farms]], they do not need to eat [[hay]] or [[grass]] to be fed overnight. This is indicated by a pecking animation while the duck floats on the surface.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Lowered purchase price from {{Price|4000}} to {{Price|1200}}.  Increased Duck Feather price from {{Price|125}} to {{Price|250}}. Ducks can now swim in water.}}\n{{History|1.5.2|Lowered sell price from {{Price|5200}} to {{Price|1560}}.}}\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Coop animals]]\n\n[[de:Ente]]\n[[es:Pato]]\n[[fr:Canard]]\n[[it:Anatra]]\n[[ja:アヒル]]\n[[ko:오리]]\n[[hu:Kacsa]]\n[[pt:Pato]]\n[[ru:Утка]]\n[[tr:Ördek]]\n[[zh:鸭]]"
